title: Readout of the Vice President's Call to Indian Prime Minister Singh | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Vice President


For Immediate Release
February 04, 2011

 



Readout of the Vice President's Call to Indian Prime Minister Singh




Vice President Biden spoke today with Indian Prime Minister Manmohan Singh to discuss regional and global issues of mutual concern.Â  The Vice President reaffirmed the U.S. commitment to building a global, strategic partnership with India.
